time was taken. We're still checking associates,'' he said, adding
that police had not established how many attackers might have been
involved or their motive.
   Neighbors said they had not seen or heard anything unusual.
   ``This has really got me shook up,'' said Nancy Martin, a
neighbor. ``This is a family street. People help each other out.
